metadata.name: A beautiful ride
metadata.description:
Life isn't always beautiful sometimes its just plain hard life can knock you down it can break your heart. 

But the struggle makes you stronger. 

And the chances make you wise. 

And happiness has its own way of taking its sweet time.

No life isn't always beautiful sometimes there will be ups and downs you will see a beautiful path after all your struggle. 

Life isn't always beautiful but its a beautiful ride.
